Vagrant
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
vagrant ssh

enter machine
vagrant provision - when you do changes inside machine
vagrant reload - when you did changes outside (e.g. adding a cookbook)

Caching in Drupal
https://www.drupal.org/node/1401522
Anonymous caching: Vagrant. Cache on admin side: Memcached. Boost not recommnded: creates duplicate paths.

NFS file system is necessary to speed up a vagrant machine.
it was developed to allow machines to mount a disk partition on a remote machine as if it were a local disk. It allows for fast, seamless sharing of files across a network.

#sudo apt-get install nfs-kernel-server nfs-common portmap


VDD
Using Chef Solo for provisioning
VLAD 
Using Ansible for provisioning
https://bitbucket.org/philipnorton42/vlad

Vagrant 1.4+ comes with the Ansible provisioning tool included so there is no need to install extra plugins.
Vagrant Perfomance: Caching
You can also install the Vagrant Cachier plugin in order to cache apt-get and gem requests, which speeds up reprovisioning.
vagrant plugin install vagrant-cachier





